<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Credex Campus Recruitment Drive</title>
    <style>
        body {
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
line-height: 1.6;
background-color: #f7f7f7;
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
}

        header {
background-color: #1976D2;
color: #fff;
text-align: center;
padding: 20px;
}

        h1 {
font-size: 36px;
margin: 0;
}

.content {
max-width: 600px;
margin: 20px auto;
background-color: #fff;
box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
border-radius: 8px;
padding: 20px;
}

p {
font-size: 16px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.button {
display: inline-block;
background-color: #1976D2;
color: #fff;
text-decoration: none;
padding: 10px 20px;
border-radius: 4px;
}

.footer {
background-color: #1976D2;
color: #fff;
text-align: center;
padding: 10px;
}

.logo {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 20px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<header>
<h1>Credex Campus Recruitment Drive</h1>
</header>

<div class="logo">
        <img src="https://example.com/credex-logo.png" alt="Credex Technology Logo" width="100" height="100">
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear ${Name},</p>

        <p>As discussed, please find attached the details of our upcoming Campus Recruitment Drive. This recruitment
            drive is exclusively for Btech(CS) & (IT) and MCA 2023 Batch students.</p>

        <p>We kindly request you to block the date <strong>${Date}</strong> for the event. We would appreciate it if
            you could send us a confirmation email to confirm your participation.</p>

        <p>Looking forward to connecting with the talented students of your esteemed institution!</p>

        <p>Regards,<br>
            ${HR}</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a class="button" href="#">Download Details</a>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Credex Technology. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
